</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/32d862a261be92079096455ce1af882eb1c15f99" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertica=
l-align: -0.338ex; width:7.122ex; height:2.343ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle b^=
{y}=3Dx.}"></span>
</p><p>For example, raising <span class=3D"texhtml">2</span> to the power o=
f <span class=3D"texhtml">3</span> gives <span class=3D"texhtml">8</span>: =
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe=
-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xm=
lns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle 2^{3}=
=3D8.}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
