"></span>
</p><p>The value of <span class=3D"texhtml">10<sup><i>x</i></sup></span> ca=
n be determined by reverse look up in the same table, since the logarithm i=
s a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Monotonic_function" title=3D"M=
