 That is, <span class=3D"texhtml">log<sub><i>b</i></sub>=E2=80=89<i>y</i></=
span> is the unique real number <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-=
style:italic;">x</span> such that <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-=
element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y"=
 style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML=
" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle b^{x}=3Dy}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
