ding the area into the yellow and blue parts. Rescaling the left hand blue =
area vertically by the factor&nbsp;<span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"fo=
nt-style:italic;">t</span> and shrinking it by the same factor horizontally=
 does not change its size. Moving it appropriately, the area fits the graph=
