/span> again. Therefore, the left hand blue area, which is the integral of =
<span class=3D"texhtml"><i>f</i>(<i>x</i>)</span> from <span class=3D"texht=
ml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">t</span> to <span class=3D"texhtml mv=
ar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">tu</span> is the same as the integral from=
 1 to <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">u</span>. T=
his justifies the equality&nbsp;(2) with a more geometric proof.
</p>
