n class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.=
org/w/index.php?title=3DLogarithm&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D19" title=
=3D"Edit section: Transcendence of the logarithm"><span>edit</span></a><spa=
n class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Real_number" title=3D"Real numb=
er">Real numbers</a> that are not <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/=
Algebraic_number" title=3D"Algebraic number">algebraic</a> are called <a hr=
ef=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transcendental_number" title=3D"Transce=
ndental number">transcendental</a>;<sup id=3D"cite_ref-46" class=3D"referen=
ce"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logarithm#cite_note-46"><span =
class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>43<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a><=
/sup> for example, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pi" title=3D"Pi=
"><span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">=CF=80</span></=
a> and <i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/E_(mathematical_constant=
)" title=3D"E (mathematical constant)">e</a></i> are such numbers, but <spa=
n class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-mat=
h-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=
=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle {\sqrt {2=
-{\sqrt {3}}}}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
        <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <msqrt>
            <mn>2</mn>
            <mo>=E2=88=92<!-- =E2=88=92 --></mo>
            <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
              <msqrt>
                <mn>3</mn>
              </msqrt>
            </mrow>
          </msqrt>
        </mrow>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle {\sqrt {2-{\s=
qrt {3}}}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/75b2a724c326f7f59f71baa9788cf455a0609bdc" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
