 title=3D"TI-83 series">TI-83 Plus</a> graphing calculator</figcaption></fi=
gure>
<p>Logarithms are easy to compute in some cases, such as <span class=3D"tex=
html">log<sub>10</sub>=E2=80=89(1000) =3D 3</span>. In general, logarithms =
can be calculated using <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Power_seri=
