=3D"texhtml">ln(<i>z</i>) =3D ln(<i>a</i>) + <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" s=
tyle=3D"font-style:italic;">b</span> =C2=B7 ln(10)</span>.
</p><p>A closely related method can be used to compute the logarithm of int=
egers. Putting <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><sp=
