pan> and <span class=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;">y</span>=
. It is obtained by repeatedly calculating the average <span class=3D"texht=
ml">(<i>x</i> + <i>y</i>)/2</span> (<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wik=
i/Arithmetic_mean" title=3D"Arithmetic mean">arithmetic mean</a>) and <span=
