t&amp;section=3D33" title=3D"Edit section: Music"><span>edit</span></a><spa=
n class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<div class=3D"thumb tmulti tright"><div class=3D"thumbinner multiimageinner=
" style=3D"width:354px;max-width:354px"><div class=3D"trow"><div class=3D"t=
